::Feline::

She blushed as he kissed her on the cheek.  She had never been kissed 
before.  She had always been the one to be doing the kissing. Now she 
was being kissed by another. It sent a shiver up her spine.  She 
wasn't sure how to take it.  But it did tell her one thing, this bot 
was hooked. She smiled to herself. One down and lots more to get, she 
thought.
"Oh, OK, the walk can wait if you have other issues to deal with.  I 
mean, don't let me occupy all your time. I don't want to get you in 
trouble."
